WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:35:14.940 --> 00:35:21.940
Today again I must thank [SOUNDS LIKE Mr.
Swanowaphala] for singing such a beautiful

00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:33.190
song about the Devi. I was very much impressed
the way Patrick told you that they are confident

00:35:39.020 --> 00:35:46.020
that they can solve any problem. That's what
it has to be. That's the sign of a Sahaja

00:35:55.999 --> 00:36:01.859
Yogi who has reached a very great height in
his understanding about himself and about

00:36:01.859 --> 00:36:05.289
others.

00:36:05.289 --> 00:36:12.289
The Chakra of the Goddess lies behind the
sternum bone in the spinal chord. This Chakra

00:36:28.850 --> 00:36:35.850
is placed above the Bhavasagara, above the
Void, as we call it in Sahaja Yoga. And the

00:36:38.200 --> 00:36:45.200
bridge that has to be crossed by the bhaktas,
by the seekers, is guarded by. She's the one,

00:37:01.210 --> 00:37:08.210
She helps Her children to come through that
passage when there are negative forces trying

00:37:15.920 --> 00:37:22.310
to attack on a seeker.

00:37:22.310 --> 00:37:29.310
This chakra is placed at the back of the sternum
bone as I told you. In childhood, the antibodies

00:37:32.530 --> 00:37:39.530
are formed in the sternum bone. They are the
warriors or the [SOUNDS LIKE Sainikas] of

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:58.280
the Devi. Until the age of 12 years they grow
and multiply, and ultimately they all get

00:38:02.540 --> 00:38:09.540
distributed all over the body, and a human
being is made able to face any outside invasion

00:38:15.630 --> 00:38:22.630
on him. These antibodies know how to fight.
They are extremely confident and they know

00:38:39.880 --> 00:38:46.880
who are their enemies. They've all these messages
built in themselves. So when the anti-God

00:38:53.730 --> 00:39:00.730
element enters into the being through any
process, say, through food, through words,

00:39:03.550 --> 00:39:10.550
through action, through devilish people, or
black magic, these antibodies combine together,

00:39:19.580 --> 00:39:26.379
collectively fight the invaders.

00:39:26.379 --> 00:39:33.379
Those who do not have their Central Heart
properly developed suffer from tremendous

00:39:40.690 --> 00:39:47.690
insecurity all their lives. When they are
children, you try to control them by frightening.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:06.880
These children later on become extremely insecure.
They are afraid of darkness, they are afraid

00:40:10.290 --> 00:40:17.290
of night. Some of them are afraid of everything.
Because the antibodies that are built in the

00:40:22.210 --> 00:40:29.210
body are not sufficient in number and being
this center so weak, the person feels extremely

00:40:34.660 --> 00:40:41.660
insecure. Later on in life when the child
goes to the school or he tries to work out

00:40:47.139 --> 00:40:54.139
something for the future, then also his confidence
can be shaken by parents, teachers, and outside

00:41:04.729 --> 00:41:11.440
people. So it is very important to understand
children who are growing.

00:41:11.440 --> 00:41:18.440
In the West they analyze everything and try
to put human beings into compartments. First

00:41:23.820 --> 00:41:30.820
the child, is a child according to them, child
has no innocence, and he's extremely selfish.

00:41:35.550 --> 00:41:42.550
Second part is adolescence, which they think
is
a very arbitrary, moody stuff. In India, we

00:41:52.030 --> 00:41:59.030
do not know that there is something like adolescence.
Now these adolescent people form a group,

00:42:00.810 --> 00:42:07.810
and they start criticizing or making fun of
all the elders. At a very young age it starts.

00:42:11.620 --> 00:42:18.620
First they make fun of the teachers, then
of the parents, then of all the people who

00:42:18.669 --> 00:42:25.669
are senior to them. They start becoming extremely
active in their brains because they see too

00:42:29.669 --> 00:42:36.669
many televisions and things like that, and
then they start behaving at a very young age

00:42:39.160 --> 00:42:44.350
in such violent ways that one cannot imagine.

00:42:44.350 --> 00:42:51.350
I used to live about 25 miles away from London.
And every time I would go to London, I would

00:42:54.460 --> 00:43:00.630
find some children doing some sort of a mischief,
somewhere. One day some of them entered into

00:43:00.630 --> 00:43:07.630
my compartment, and they started pulling out
all the covers, thrusting their knives into

00:43:12.660 --> 00:43:19.660
the seats, opening out all the upholstery.
I was just sitting and watching. So I said,

00:43:24.530 --> 00:43:31.530
"Now are you tired? Please sit down. What's
the problem?" They said, "We are all very

00:43:31.979 --> 00:43:37.240
angry." I said, "For what? Why are you angry?"
Said, "We are just angry." I said, "But you

00:43:37.240 --> 00:43:44.240
have to be angry for something." They were
children going to good schools definitely,

00:43:49.580 --> 00:43:56.130
wearing very good clothes. And then I had
to, - when the train stopped - I called the

00:43:56.130 --> 00:43:59.470
ticket collector and told him that these boys
have been doing all this hooliganic, hooliganism

00:43:59.470 --> 00:44:06.470
in the compartment and you better look at
it. And he came in and he said, "this is a

00:44:10.480 --> 00:44:15.410
common thing" and then somehow or other he
took them out.

00:44:15.410 --> 00:44:22.410
But the only thing I felt about them is, that
all of them had their Center Heart catching.

00:44:24.270 --> 00:44:31.270
On the Kundalini, they were catching their
Center Heart. But when they saw Me, they sat

00:44:32.620 --> 00:44:39.620
down. They were quiet, they listened to Me.
I settled their Center Heart. And most of

00:44:45.709 --> 00:44:51.770
them said, "We are angry with our mother."
"Why?" "Because our brothers are angry." "But

00:44:51.770 --> 00:44:58.770
why your brothers are angry?" Then I discovered
that Freud has given these funny ideas against

00:44:59.470 --> 00:45:06.470
the mother. Mother itself, can you imagine!
What a anti-God activity it is.

00:45:06.760 --> 00:45:13.760
To an Indian, Mother is the primal thing - any
Indian. Because his sense of security lies

00:45:19.510 --> 00:45:26.510
in the mother. Even if the father is hot-tempered,
is angry, still they depend on the mother.

00:45:33.600 --> 00:45:40.600
Because mother knows when to get angry and
when not to get angry. She has the discrimination.

00:45:40.959 --> 00:45:46.950
And she is the one who protects them.

00:45:46.950 --> 00:45:53.950
The idea of Mother is completely blasted in
the West, and this is the reason why the children

00:45:55.480 --> 00:46:02.480
of that country feel so insecure, and when
they grow, they are extremely insecure. You

00:46:03.680 --> 00:46:10.680
won't believe that all the time they are polishing
their brass, cleaning their house, but not

00:46:12.410 --> 00:46:19.350
even a rat enters their houses. And if they
have to talk to someone, they'll make a person

00:46:19.350 --> 00:46:24.880
stand outside and talk from inside, specially
in London, because they are literally frightened.

00:46:24.880 --> 00:46:31.880
Nobody will believe, the British who ruled
us, are such frightened people. But they are.

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:38.160
They are frightened of each other, they are
frightened of themselves. The reason is, the

00:46:38.160 --> 00:46:42.140
Center Heart is absolutely weak.

00:46:42.140 --> 00:46:49.140
I've told you the first reason, the family
insecurities. The child does not know when

00:46:50.540 --> 00:46:57.540
he comes back from school, whether his mother
would be there or she would be gone. They

00:46:59.920 --> 00:47:06.920
don't have mothers who can bear a lot from
the husbands and smile and show no signs of

00:47:08.230 --> 00:47:14.540
their agony to their children. But the mothers
in that country, I've seen, always try to

00:47:14.540 --> 00:47:21.540
use their children from all kinds of emotional
blackmail, you can call it. They try to torture

00:47:22.589 --> 00:47:28.649
the child by telling all the things the husband
is doing to them and whatever is the problem

00:47:28.649 --> 00:47:35.649
they are facing with the husbands. So the
child is not secured by the mother, but, on

00:47:35.910 --> 00:47:42.910
the contrary, child starts giving security
to mother there. At a very young age it starts,

00:47:43.100 --> 00:47:50.100
and the child becomes extremely negative and
left-sided. He feels that he's born in a place

00:47:52.070 --> 00:47:56.279
full of hatred, insecurity, and fear.

00:47:56.279 --> 00:48:03.279
When the bhaktas are born in those countries,
they are also the same way. Because they think

00:48:04.760 --> 00:48:11.760
if they have to go to a Guru, the Guru, as
known so far, tortures them or extracts all

00:48:12.550 --> 00:48:19.529
the money, takes their [SOUNDS LIKE pareeksha,
tess], and he sometimes leaves them high and

00:48:19.529 --> 00:48:24.399
dry on the streets.

00:48:24.399 --> 00:48:31.399
But in our country the Goddess has taken Incarnation
many a times. Thousands time She has taken

00:48:33.510 --> 00:48:40.510
here Her birth, whenever the bhaktas called
Her, when they are pestered by the negative

00:48:42.350 --> 00:48:49.350
force, She came on this Earth to save them.
These things used to be just accepted by people,

00:48:55.839 --> 00:49:02.839
but never were really accepted in their hearts.
People thought these are some sorts of mythological

00:49:07.899 --> 00:49:14.660
stories that the Goddess came on this Earth
and She tried to save the people. They could

00:49:14.660 --> 00:49:21.630
not believe that there could be a Shakti who
could be born, who could fight these horrible

00:49:21.630 --> 00:49:28.630
rakshasas, and kill them, and save Her children,
Her bhaktas, from agony. It was too much.

00:49:31.350 --> 00:49:38.350
But today in Sahaja Yoga, you have seen that
when Kundalini rises and stops at the Center

00:49:40.800 --> 00:49:47.800
Nabhi, you have to say the mantra of 'Jagadamba',
and the Kundalini rises. That means, She resides

00:49:52.130 --> 00:49:59.130
in the Center Heart, and when She is being
worshipped, the Kundalini rises. This center

00:50:08.730 --> 00:50:15.730
has got twelve petals. But the Goddess has
thousand hands and thousand eyes. She has

00:50:29.950 --> 00:50:36.950
16,000 Naris to work out Her different aspects
of enlightenment. But the first thing She

00:50:43.990 --> 00:50:50.990
has to do, through Her generosity, and kindness,
and compassion, and patience, She has to suck

00:50:53.480 --> 00:51:00.480
in the sins - the [SOUNDS LIKE Papavimochini]
- the sins of human beings.

00:51:03.199 --> 00:51:10.199
One of the sentences in Bible was, "Wages
of fear is sin." Or you can put it the other

00:51:14.899 --> 00:51:21.899
way round, "The wages of sin is fear." If
you have fear, you are committing a sin against

00:51:29.760 --> 00:51:36.760
your Self and against God. Because, if Mother
is Almighty, and She can solve all your problems,

00:51:42.089 --> 00:51:47.860
you are under Her protection, then why should
you have any fear? That means you do not believe

00:51:47.860 --> 00:51:54.860
that She's that powerful. When a person is
frightened, this center start breathing fast,

00:52:01.149 --> 00:52:08.149
giving rhythmic instructions to all the antibodies.
With that you feel you are getting a palpitation

00:52:17.429 --> 00:52:24.429
in the heart. This palpitation is nothing
but a signal to all the antibodies to fight

00:52:28.499 --> 00:52:33.049
the emergency of an attack.

00:52:33.049 --> 00:52:40.049
But when somebody builds up insecurity later
on in life, it becomes a physical problem.

00:52:49.149 --> 00:52:56.149
If they have insecurities earlier, it is an
emotional problem. But later on in life, when

00:52:57.690 --> 00:53:04.690
one develops a insecurity - any kind, like
a wife is insecure about her husband; husband

00:53:06.789 --> 00:53:13.789
is a loafer or a bad man, and carrying on
with other women, so the motherhood of the

00:53:17.090 --> 00:53:24.090
wife is challenged. And when her motherhood
is challenged, she may get the weakening of

00:53:25.919 --> 00:53:32.919
this center, by which she may suffer quite
a lot and may have even breast cancer. These

00:53:33.259 --> 00:53:40.259
insecurities can be also self-made, imaginary.
People can just think about it and build up

00:53:40.720 --> 00:53:47.720
some sort of insecurities, which are of no
actual existence.

00:53:50.139 --> 00:53:57.139
But such fears are very much more in the West.
Because the life in the West has no mooring,

00:54:02.309 --> 00:54:06.979
has no explanation. Whatever you ask them,
they'll say, "What's wrong?" A husband will

00:54:06.979 --> 00:54:13.269
say, "What's wrong?" in having a keep. And
the wife will also say, "All right, if he

00:54:13.269 --> 00:54:18.830
wants to have a keep, let him have it." In
