00:54:18.830 --> 00:54:25.830
She would starve, she would do everything,
but she will never touch a man who has a keep.

00:54:29.159 --> 00:54:36.159
So the basis of the strength of Indian women
is their sense of chastity. The sense of chastity

00:54:42.479 --> 00:54:49.479
in the Indian women is so great that nothing
can deter them as long as they are chaste.

00:54:52.489 --> 00:54:59.489
But if they are not chaste, then fear settles
in them very fast. Chastity is the strength

