being challenged. A woman who is frightened
that her chastity may be disturbed, also can

00:55:25.739 --> 00:55:32.739
develop a problem with the Heart Chakra. Such
women can develop breast cancers, breathing

00:55:42.169 --> 00:55:49.169
troubles, and other kind of frightening diseases
