00:56:10.739 --> 00:56:17.739
a woman. But if she's not a woman, she doesn't
feel much, and she just behaves in a very

00:56:19.580 --> 00:56:26.580
manly way. And that's what I've seen in the
West, that women really don't much care when

00:56:27.720 --> 00:56:34.720
their children die. But it is because they
are not women. If you are a woman you definitely

