00:56:45.859 --> 00:56:52.210
and she accepts the life as it is, for the
sake of her husband, or may be if she has

00:56:52.210 --> 00:56:59.210
more relations or other children. She becomes
extremely powerful as a reaction to what has

00:57:00.549 --> 00:57:04.279
happened to her.

00:57:04.279 --> 00:57:11.279
That's only possible if your center of Heart
is all right. Such women do not grudge, do

00:57:14.789 --> 00:57:21.249
not complain, are extremely serene, and can
bear up lots of things. They are extremely

00:57:21.249 --> 00:57:28.249
tolerant and can go to any extent to help
their children, but they are never spoiling

00:57:31.099 --> 00:57:37.820
their children. They never spoil their children,
because they understand spoiling is much worse

00:57:37.820 --> 00:57:44.450
than beating the child. They never spoil the
children, nor ever pamper them, and never

00:57:44.450 --> 00:57:51.259
get dominated by their children. They know,
"I have to guide the child and have to look

00:57:51.259 --> 00:57:57.779
after the child." So they look after all the
ideals and righteousness and the virtues of

00:57:57.779 --> 00:58:04.779
the child. And if he tries to get out of it,
they go all out to win him over back to virtue

00:58:07.340 --> 00:58:14.340
and to better life. But those people, those
women, who do not care for actual growth of

00:58:18.109 --> 00:58:22.779
the child, may just avoid it and escape it.

00:58:22.779 --> 00:58:29.779
In the men, this chakra is caught up if they
have lost their mother very early, or if their

00:58:31.669 --> 00:58:38.669
mother by chance is a very cruel woman. Also
this chakra can be caught up by men, if they

00:58:41.299 --> 00:58:48.299
have been to wars, and if they have seen frightful
things in the war. Such people could be extremely

00:58:50.379 --> 00:58:57.379
emotional and could be easily befooled by
people who try to win over their emotions.

00:59:05.590 --> 00:59:12.590
What is to be done to improve this chakra?
In Sahaja Yoga we have many techniques by

00:59:12.799 --> 00:59:19.799
which we can improve this chakra, and get
your confidence back. As Patrick has said

00:59:19.940 --> 00:59:26.940
- that he never used to speak. And I have
seen many actors who act very well and when

00:59:28.639 --> 00:59:33.559
they came to My program, they said, "Mother
please don't ask us to speak because we just

00:59:33.559 --> 00:59:38.739
don't know how to speak. We can act, but we
cannot speak to people." They tried once or

00:59:38.739 --> 00:59:45.739
twice and they ended up with two-three sentences,
mumbled down and sat down. I found out all

00:59:47.149 --> 00:59:54.149
of them had this Chakra very badly damaged.
